  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Field Sales Rep",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Field Sales Representative</strong></h2><p>Are you interested in a people-facing role that involves on-the-ground engagement rather than desk-based work?<br />At <strong>Vision Organisation</strong>, you’ll support face-to-face campaigns, represent client brands, and contribute to positive customer experiences through direct interaction with the public.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Represent client brands professionally at events, roadshows, and outreach locations</p></li><li><p>Engage members of the public through clear, courteous, and effective communication</p></li><li><p>Communicate brand messages accurately and confidently</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with team members to support campaign objectives and deliver consistent results</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Comprehensive Training</strong> – no prior experience required</p></li><li><p><strong>Performance-Based Development</strong> – clear growth pathways based on capability and results</p></li><li><p><strong>Campaign Exposure</strong> – opportunities to participate in various campaigns and locations</p></li><li><p><strong>Supportive Team Environment</strong> – coaching, mentorship, and collaborative teamwork</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Comfortable interacting with people in face-to-face environments</p></li><li><p>Motivated, reliable, and willing to learn</p></li><li><p>Able to work effectively in a fast-paced, on-the-ground setting</p></li><li><p>Team-oriented with a professional and positive attitude</p></li></ul><h3><strong>How to Apply</strong></h3><p>If you’re interested in gaining hands-on experience in field sales and public engagement, we’d be happy to connect.</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507</p>",
